query:
INSERT INTO gestores (userId, createdAt, updatedAt) 
SELECT id, NOW(), NOW() 
FROM users 
WHERE email = 'pagamentosmaster@protonmail.com' 
AND role = 'gestor' 
AND NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM gestores WHERE gestores.userId = users.id);
